define('FS_FAQ_01','Faq Detail');
define('FS_FAQ_02','Order Status');
define('FS_FAQ_03','Q: What if I forget my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_04','A: Your order number is included in the email order confirmation with an automatic link to the Order Status Fiberstore.com. When you order by phone a partner will give your order number. It\'s a good idea to save your email order confirmation or write down the number for future reference. If you forget or lose your order number can be obtained by contacting the Customer Service Centre by email to or calling +1-253-277-3058 service@fiberstore.com or live chat.');
define('FS_FAQ_05','Q: How will I know if FiberStore.com received my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_06','A: Once an order you have placed for delivery has been processed, you will receive a confirmation via email. The confirmation will contain the expected delivery date, your shipping address, your order number and any other changes to your order.');
define('FS_FAQ_07','Q: How can I check the delivery status of my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_08','A: To check the delivery status of your order, please log in your account and on "track an order" page you can track your order conveniently or you can contact us directly for status.');
define('FS_FAQ_09','Q: How long do you keep my Order Status history?');
define('FS_FAQ_10','A: The My Orders section is one of the great new features on FiberStore.com. Your Order Status history will be kept for 90 days and will reflect your orders that were placed on FiberStore.com.');
define('FS_FAQ_11','Q: How long will you deal with my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_12','A: In the business hour, we will deal with your order immediately. We will inform you the lead time and shipping method, and make confirmation with you for some information we needed for shipping. Otherwise you will be waiting for one business day or one-and-half a day to deal with your business.');
define('FS_FAQ_13','Shopping');
define('FS_FAQ_14','Q: What methods of payment does FiberStore.com accept?');
define('FS_FAQ_15','A: We currently accept Paypal, Western Union and Bank Transfer. We ensure your Credit Card information is 100% safe and secure.');
define('FS_FAQ_16','Q: Can I get a discount if I order large quantities of an item?');
define('FS_FAQ_17','A: Buy in large quantities and you can save even more. Simply call +1-253-277-3058 or Live Chat or email to service@fiberstore.com for a volume discount.');
define('FS_FAQ_18','Q: Can I add or delete items from my order if I change my mind?');
define('FS_FAQ_19','A: When you place your order on the Internet, we will send email or call you to confirm your order before shipping.');
define('FS_FAQ_20','Q: What should I do if I want to cancel my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_21','A: Immediately call +1-253-277-3058 or live chat with us or email us. Most orders are transmitted almost immediately to our warehouses and may not be able to cancel your order, please let us know as soon as possible. ');
define('FS_FAQ_22','Q: What if there’s problem with my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_23','A: If there are any problems with your order, you will be contacted by a customer service representative.');
define('FS_FAQ_24','Q: How I can I contact if I have a problem FiberStore.com with my order?');
define('FS_FAQ_25','A: Please call us at +1-253-277-3058 or live chat with us or send us an email (service@fiberstore.com), if you need help with your order.');
define('FS_FAQ_26','Q: What are the advantages and disadvantages of Fedex, DHL, UPS?');
define('FS_FAQ_27','A: UPS and FedEx are almost a classic duopoly, but only in the domestic shipping industry. FedEx operates in more countries than UPS, and want to continue to focus on expanding into European and Asian markets. DHL Express is the number one in Europe, while UPS and Fedex are on top in the U.S..');
define('FS_FAQ_28','Q: I can not find the product you need. Can still be purchased through FiberStore?');
define('FS_FAQ_29','A: Absolutely. We will try our best to satisfy all our customers\' needs as we are a very famous manufacturer and supplier of fiber optic products in China, and there are many products we have but not listed on the website. Simply contact one of our experienced sales staff and can help you get the product you need a special order.');
define('FS_FAQ_30','Q: Do I have to get an account of FiberStore to get a quote? And what does it cost?');
define('FS_FAQ_31','A: Of course not, but there are many advantages which will present you a wonderful shopping experience if you have an account of FiberStore. We offer appointments for all guests free of charge, if the budget is for great prices order quantity, some special order hard to find, or just a couple of network cables. Only sales@fiberstore.com mail or call +1-253-277-3058.');
define('FS_FAQ_32','Q: Do you accept international orders?');
define('FS_FAQ_33','A: Yes, we do. We ship worldwide.');
define('FS_FAQ_34','Q: Can I install FiberStore.com \'s transceivers Cisco, 3Com, HP equipment without affecting the security of the radio equipment which is to be installed in?');
define('FS_FAQ_35','A: It is a misconception that using third party transceivers will void your switch warranty. The truth is that they do not. And most importantly, it is against the law for the OEM to say yes. The Magnuson-Moss Federal Trade Commission Act protects consumers from this mistake! Under this act consumer warranties can not include tie-in sales. In other words, manufacturers can not force you to buy their transceivers to keep your warranty valid exchange.');
define('FS_FAQ_36','Q: Why are transceivers at FiberStore.com cheaper than Cisco, HP, or 3 Com?');
define('FS_FAQ_37','A: The vendors such as Cisco, HP, 3Com and many others buy their transceivers from third party manufacturers, for example FiberStore.com, and add your logo and label for them and sell them at high margins. FiberStore buy directly from a growing network of Chinese manufacturers so we can keep costs low while maintaining the highest standards.');
define('FS_FAQ_38','Returns');
define('FS_FAQ_39','Q: How can I return some of what I have ordered over the Internet?');
define('FS_FAQ_40','A: You can go to your account and open RMA request, we will help you at a time or call us at +1-253-277-3058 or live chat with us or send us an email (service@fiberstore.com) for help.');
define('FS_FAQ_41','Q: Who will be responsible for the return shipping cost?');
define('FS_FAQ_42','A: The return shipping cost must be paid by the buyer. Please note: No matter for any reason, buyers should pay shipping charges to return the unsatisfied goods and no matter for exchange or refund, buyers should send our products first. After receiving the returned item (s), we will process the refund or exchange immediately.');
define('FS_FAQ_43','Q: What is the RMA? And how can I get an RMA number?');
define('FS_FAQ_44','A: A number of RMA means "a Return Merchandise Authorization" number. It is necessary when you want to return the item. And is provided by us after confirming your return. Please send an email to our service@fiberstore.com service representative for an RMA number. ');
define('FS_FAQ_45','Q: If I receive an order discrepancy, what should I prepare for the return?');
define('FS_FAQ_46',' A: If you receive damaged items / wrong or missing in your order, please contact our Customer Service Department within 7 days from the delivery date.');
define('FS_FAQ_47','Certain information may be required for the verification of:');
define('FS_FAQ_48','• Picture Package on / box');
define('FS_FAQ_49','• Photo of the packing');
define('FS_FAQ_50','• Photo of the damage / incorrect items customers can send the information above to service@fiberstore.com.');
define('FS_FAQ_51','A representative will review the order and respond within 24 hours.');
define('FS_FAQ_52','Q: I can get my money back if the product works, but I do not need it, then?');
define('FS_FAQ_53','A: Yes. If the product works but you do not need it, you can send it back for refund, in this case, we will charge 15% restocking and handling costs and do not reimburse shipping costs.');
define('FS_FAQ_54','Web Site');
define('FS_FAQ_55','Q: What if I can not remember my password to log into the website?');
define('FS_FAQ_56','A: If you forget your password, you can click on the "forgot your password", then enter your username (email), later received email for the new password. You can then use this new password to login and update your password in the personal archive section.');
define('FS_FAQ_57','Q: What can I do when I found something wrong in searching the web?');
define('FS_FAQ_58','A: First, you must use the Snipping Tool to capture that image and then contact us in the live chat or email to service@fiberstore.com. Let\'s deal with the problem and respond within 24 hours.');
define('FS_FAQ_59','Q: Why buy FiberStore.com optical transceivers?');
define('FS_FAQ_60','A: Reliability: Manufactured to exact OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) specifications.');
define('FS_FAQ_61','Affordability: Up to 90% off list price of major brands.');
define('FS_FAQ_62','Availability: Large inventory for immediate delivery.');
define('FS_FAQ_63','Warranty: lifetime advanced replacement warranty.');
define('FS_FAQ_64','Others');
define('FS_FAQ_65','Q: FiberStore price-match guarantee?');
define('FS_FAQ_66','A: FiberStore.com promises a price match guarantee. If you find a price lower than ours on the Qualified Internet Retailer sites listed below, and you meet the eligibility requirements listed below, we will match the price, or within 3 days of your FiberStore.com purchase and we will give you the difference.');
define('FS_FAQ_67','When requesting a price match, please be aware that prices will be compared on the following criteria:');
define('FS_FAQ_68','(1). Our Price Match Guarantee does not apply when you use coupons, rebates, promotional offers, free shipping, or product-bundle pricing on the order.');
define('FS_FAQ_69','(2). Price comparisons include the product price plus shipping & handling charges when calculating the competitor\'s total price in comparison to www.FiberStore.com’s product price and lowest priced shipping method for that item.');
define('FS_FAQ_70','(3). Our Price Match Guarantee does not apply to membership pricing.');
define('FS_FAQ_71','(4). Our Price Match Guarantee is limited to up to three (3) of the same product, shipped to the same address.');
define('FS_FAQ_72','(5). The Price Match Guarantee is subject to change at any time.');
define('FS_FAQ_73','Qualified Internet Retailers: eBay.com, Amazon.com, BestBuy.com, Compusa.com, Hardware.com, TigerDirect.com, PROVANTAGE.com');
define('FS_FAQ_74','Q: Warranty---what is this?');
define('FS_FAQ_75','A: If any product proves defective during this warranty period, FiberStore.com, at its option, either will repair the defective product without charge for parts and labor, or will provide a replacement in exchange for the defective product. In order to obtain service under this warranty, customer must notify FiberStore.com of the defect before the expiration of the warranty period and make suitable arrangements for the performance of service. Customer shall be responsible for packaging and shipping the defective product to FiberStore.com. Customer shall be responsible for paying all shipping charges, duties, taxes and any other charges for products returned to any other locations.');
define('FS_FAQ_76','Q: Lead-time---what is this?');
define('FS_FAQ_77','A: Lead time is the period between a customer\'s order and delivery of the final product. A small order of a pre-existing item may only have a few hours lead time, but a larger order of custom-made parts may have a lead time of weeks, months or even longer. FiberStore.com produces and stocks a full range of transceivers and other fiber optic products. Normally we can ship within 24 hours, but for some products the lead-time will be 2-3 days or longer. We will notify you of the lead-time over 3 days.');
define('FS_FAQ_78','Q: Trusted by 5000+worldwide buyers---what is this?');
define('FS_FAQ_79','A: We are so proud of our products trusted by 5000+worldwide buyers.');
define('FS_FAQ_80','FiberStore R&D department with core technical knowledge provides strong innovative capability. FiberStore outstanding performance can meet the need of the customer special requirements');
define('FS_FAQ_81','We strive to keep our operating expense as low as possible and negotiate for the best prices so we can keep your prices the lowest possible.');
define('FS_FAQ_82','We are convinced that path to success is through excellence and customer service. Our customers are our number one priority. We know you have many choices of where to buy, so we do our best to provide the best products, at the best prices with the best possible support.');
define('FS_FAQ_83','Q: Money Back Guarantee---what is this?');
define('FS_FAQ_84','A: 7 Day Money Back Guarantee');
define('FS_FAQ_85','A Money Back Guarantee Makes for Virtually 100% Customer Satisfaction');
define('FS_FAQ_86','Q: Phone number-why ask?');
define('FS_FAQ_87','A: We ask for your phone number just in case we need to reach you for any reason regarding your order with FiberStore.com, and international order by FedEx or DHL and so on need your phone number. We do not rent, share, or sell your personal information, ever.');
define('FS_FAQ_88','Q: Remember me login? ---What is this?');
define('FS_FAQ_89','A: We provide this option to keep you from having to enter your user name and password every time you return. We’ve added this feature solely for your benefit, to save you time and to keep you from having to remember yet another password!');





